                                     1990    1991    1992*
Consumption:
OECD countries                      325.7   308.3   304.2
World                               645.5   615.7   606.8
Crude production:
OECD countries                      382.5   367.2   362.7
World                               770.2   731.9   723.2
OECD countries trade balance        -12.3   -18.2   -17.4
