FT  13 JUL 92 / World News in Brief: Loch Ness survey
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A sonar exploration of Loch Ness, expected to discover species new to
science, begins today. The last underwater survey, in 1903, was carried out
from a rowing boat using a lead weight and a piece of piano wire.
