1951: Graduated from Tokyo University economics department
1954: Joined Seibu Department Stores
1961: President of Seibu Department Stores
1975: Chairman of Seibu Allstate Life Insurance
1987: President of Saison Corporation
1991: Chairman of Saison Corporation
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Other posts include board member of Keidanren, board member of the
international council of The Museum of Modern Art, guest professor of
